ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of JOHN McBAIN of Ottawa, Ontario, as President and Chief Executive Officer of Canada Lands Company Limited, to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months, or until such time as a new President and Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective September 3, 2020.
